BT
/F1 10 Tf
50 760 Td
13 TL
() Tj
T*
(Then:) Tj
T*
(- TPS ~= \(Bv * F\) / \(T * Savg\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Use this as a planning model, not a guarantee. Real block composition, propagation, and tx mix) Tj
T*
(always influence observed throughput.) Tj
T*
(- Current Reference vsize Profiles) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Representative estimates \(compressed witness, no metadata-heavy edge cases\):) Tj
T*
(- 1 in / 1 out: ~513 vB) Tj
T*
(- 1 in / 2 out: ~566 vB) Tj
T*
(- 2 in / 2 out: ~615 vB) Tj
T*
(- 3 in / 2 out: ~664 vB) Tj
T*
(- 4 in / 2 out: ~713 vB) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(These are useful baseline points for fee estimation and capacity planning. Production) Tj
T*
(applications should still measure real rolling averages from their own observed workload.) Tj
T*
(- Example TPS Bands) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(With T = 120:) Tj
T*
(- at 566 vB: 51.5 TPS ideal, 49.0 TPS at F=0.95) Tj
T*
(- at 615 vB: 47.4 TPS ideal, 45.1 TPS at F=0.95) Tj
T*
(- at 664 vB: 43.9 TPS ideal, 41.7 TPS at F=0.95) Tj
T*
(- at 713 vB: 40.9 TPS ideal, 38.8 TPS at F=0.95) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Private flows are intentionally larger than public-only flows and therefore reduce effective TPS) Tj
T*
(for privacy-heavy block compositions.) Tj
T*
(- Why vsize Discipline Matters) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Sizing discipline directly affects:) Tj
T*
(- fair fee market behavior,) Tj
T*
(- predictable miner packing,) Tj
T*
(- mempool anti-spam controls,) Tj
T*
(- reliable cost estimation for wallets and API clients.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If two components disagree on vsize, they may disagree on minimum fee validity or replacement) Tj
T*
(eligibility. That creates avoidable UX and propagation failures.) Tj
T*
(- Operational Validation Workflow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When updating tx serialization or witness rules:) Tj
T*
(- recalculate vsize metrics from live serializer output,) Tj
T*
(- run mempool admission tests for floor and minimum fee boundaries,) Tj
T*
(- compare block packing behavior under mixed tx shapes,) Tj
T*
(- verify explorer/API displayed vsize matches internal policy computation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Related docs:) Tj
T*
(- Docs/Tx.md) Tj
T*
(- Docs/Consensus.md) Tj
T*
(- Docs/Network_Stack.md) Tj
T*
(- Policy Snapshot Coupled to Sizing) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Sizing assumptions in this doc align with active policy:) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
